<meta name="sailthru.title" content="There&#039;s No Such Thing as One True Love. Here&#039;s Why That&#039;s Awesome" />
<link href="http://greatist.com/happiness/no-such-thing-as-one-true-love" rel="canonical" />
<script type="application/ld+json">
